control arduino servo with xbox controller
xaxis	controls xaxis servo	3	SLIDER	z	0	-1.0	0.1
yaxis	controls yaxis servo	3	SLIDER	rz	0	1.0	0.1
xleft	moves position left	1	BUTTON	3	0	0.0	0.0
xright	moves position right	1	BUTTON	1	0	0.0	0.0
yup	moves postion up	1	BUTTON	4	0	0.0	0.0
ydown	moves position down	1	BUTTON	0	0	0.0	0.0
widen	widens fov	1	BUTTON	6	0	0.0	0.0
narrow	narrows fov	1	BUTTON	7	0	0.0	0.0
invertTrue	sets control inversion to true	1	BUTTON	10	0	0.0	0.0
invertFalse	sets control inversion to false	1	BUTTON	11	0	0.0	0.0
